{
  "text": "I didn't mean to cover previously covered material. It was just that I was trying to work into a better understanding of what we're talking about with the background of the bailing process. And what I was actually attempting to do was to discover something new in asking the question. So please, if I ask any questions in the future that have already been covered, don't bother to repeat the material. I'm just searching in the same area for the possibility of greater enlightenment with respect to a particular area since it seems to be one of the major areas of experience in our present condition of Bailey that produces a very large amount of catalyst. And I'm trying to understand or to use a poor term, how this bailing process created for the or created a greater experience and how this experience evolved, shall I say? The questions are very difficult at times to ask. And was this uh uh shall we say known by uh in in some minimal way, you might say, by those who uh devised these statues and drawings, etc. And there is of course much other a distortion involved in a discussion of any mystic archetypical form, however we may answer in the primitive and note that you are perceptive.",
